(CUSTOMER SUPPORT POLICY) Tj
T*
(Last updated: January 2025) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(OVERVIEW) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Our goal is to provide fast, effective, and friendly support for every customer. This) Tj
T*
(document explains the support channels available to you, our response time) Tj
T*
(commitments, how we prioritize requests, and how to get the most out of your support) Tj
T*
(interactions.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(1. SUPPORT CHANNELS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.1 Live Chat) Tj
T*
(Available on our website and mobile app. Live chat connects you directly with a) Tj
T*
(support agent during business hours. Our average first-response time via chat is) Tj
T*
(under 2 minutes. After business hours, chat is handled by our AI assistant, which can) Tj
T*
(resolve common issues instantly. Complex after-hours requests are escalated to a) Tj
T*
(human agent and resolved by the start of the next business day.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(To access live chat: click the chat bubble icon at the bottom right of any page on) Tj
T*
(our website or tap "Support" in the mobile app menu.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.2 Email Support) Tj
T*
(Email us at support@shopexample.com. We respond to all emails within 24 hours on) Tj
T*
(business days. For faster routing, include your order number in the subject line.) Tj
T*
(Email support is best suited for non-urgent issues, detailed inquiries, attaching) Tj
T*
(photos or documents, and tracking ongoing cases.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.3 Phone Support) Tj
T*
(Phone support is available Monday through Friday, 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM \(Eastern Time\).) Tj
T*
(Toll-free number: 1-800-555-0199) Tj
T*
(Our average hold time is under 5 minutes. For complex issues, we may offer a callback) Tj
T*
(rather than placing you on hold.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.4 Help Center \(Self-Service\)) Tj
T*
(Our Help Center at help.shopexample.com contains hundreds of articles, step-by-step) Tj
T*
(guides, and video tutorials. Topics include order management, returns, account) Tj
T*
(settings, payment methods, and product use. Most common questions can be answered) Tj
T*
(without contacting an agent.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.5 Community Forum) Tj
T*
(Our community forum allows customers to share tips, ask questions, and connect with) Tj
T*
(other users. Forum moderators and our team monitor the forum and respond to) Tj
T*
(unanswered questions within 2 business days. The forum is not monitored for urgent) Tj
T*
(issues.) Tj
ET
endstream
