(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(2. BUSINESS HOURS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Live chat \(human agents\): Monday to Friday, 8:00 AM to 8:00 PM Eastern Time) Tj
T*
(Phone support: Monday to Friday, 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM Eastern Time) Tj
T*
(Email response window: Within 24 hours on business days) Tj
T*
(AI assistant \(chat\): Available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week) Tj
T*
(Help Center: Available 24/7) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(We observe the following U.S. public holidays, during which human support is) Tj
T*
(unavailable \(AI and Help Center remain available\):) Tj
T*
(- New Year's Day) Tj
T*
(- Memorial Day) Tj
T*
(- Independence Day \(July 4\)) Tj
T*
(- Labor Day) Tj
T*
(- Thanksgiving Day) Tj
T*
(- Christmas Day) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(On days immediately preceding or following a major holiday, response times may be) Tj
T*
(extended.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(3. RESPONSE TIME COMMITMENTS \(SLAs\)) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(We categorize support requests by urgency:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.1 Critical \(Response within 1 hour during business hours\)) Tj
T*
(- Payment failures or unauthorized charges) Tj
T*
(- Account compromised or suspected fraud) Tj
T*
(- Order shipped to wrong address \(high value orders\)) Tj
T*
(- Unable to access account and time-sensitive order pending) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.2 High Priority \(Response within 4 hours during business hours\)) Tj
T*
(- Order arrived significantly damaged) Tj
T*
(- Missing items from a delivered order) Tj
T*
(- Incorrect item received) Tj
T*
(- Subscription billing error) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.3 Standard \(Response within 24 hours\)) Tj
T*
(- General product questions) Tj
T*
(- Return and refund status inquiries) Tj
