(4. SUPPORT TIERS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.1 Standard Support) Tj
T*
(Available to all customers. Includes access to all support channels during business) Tj
T*
(hours, the Help Center, and community forum.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.2 Priority Support \(Premium Customers\)) Tj
T*
(Customers with an active premium subscription or qualifying order history receive) Tj
T*
(Priority Support, which includes:) Tj
T*
(- Dedicated phone queue with shorter hold times) Tj
T*
(- Priority handling in the live chat queue) Tj
T*
(- Assigned case manager for ongoing complex issues) Tj
T*
(- Response time SLAs upgraded by one tier \(e.g., Standard issues resolved within 8) Tj
T*
(hours instead of 24\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(To check if your account qualifies for Priority Support, log in and go to Account >) Tj
T*
(Membership & Benefits.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.3 Business and Enterprise Support) Tj
T*
(Customers with a Business or Enterprise plan receive a dedicated account manager,) Tj
T*
(24/7 phone support, and a guaranteed 4-hour response SLA on all issue categories.) Tj
T*
(Contact your account manager or email enterprise@shopexample.com for support.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(5. HOW TO SUBMIT AN EFFECTIVE SUPPORT REQUEST) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Providing the right information upfront speeds up resolution. Include:) Tj
T*
(- Your order number \(format: ORD-XXXXXXX\)) Tj
T*
(- The email address associated with your account) Tj
T*
(- A clear description of the issue \(what happened, when, and what you expected\)) Tj
T*
(- Screenshots or photos, if applicable) Tj
T*
(- What you have already tried) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The more context you provide, the faster we can help without back-and-forth.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(6. CASE MANAGEMENT AND ESCALATION) Tj
ET
