(6.1 Case Numbers) Tj
T*
(Every support request receives a unique case number. Reference this number in all) Tj
T*
(follow-up communications to ensure continuity. Case numbers are sent in the) Tj
T*
(confirmation email or chat transcript.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6.2 Escalation Process) Tj
T*
(If you are not satisfied with a resolution or feel your issue has not been addressed) Tj
T*
(properly, you may request escalation in any of the following ways:) Tj
T*
(- Reply to your support email and type "ESCALATE" in the subject line) Tj
T*
(- Ask the live chat agent to transfer you to a supervisor) Tj
T*
(- Call 1-800-555-0199 and press 9 at any time during the menu for escalation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(A senior agent or team lead will review your case and follow up within 2 to 4) Tj
T*
(business hours.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6.3 Dispute Resolution) Tj
T*
(If an escalation does not resolve your issue to your satisfaction, you may submit a) Tj
T*
(formal dispute by emailing disputes@shopexample.com. Formal disputes are reviewed by) Tj
T*
(our Customer Experience leadership team within 5 business days.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(7. ACCESSIBILITY SUPPORT) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(We are committed to supporting customers with disabilities. Options include:) Tj
T*
(- TTY/TDD: 1-800-555-0200 \(relay service available\)) Tj
T*
(- Large-print instructions available on request) Tj
T*
(- Alt text and screen reader compatibility on our website) Tj
T*
(- Extended response time accommodations for customers who need more time to provide) Tj
T*
(information) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Contact us to discuss your accessibility needs, and we will do our best to) Tj
T*
(accommodate.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(8. PRIVACY IN SUPPORT INTERACTIONS) Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(All support interactions are handled in accordance with our Privacy Policy. We may) Tj
T*
(record phone calls and save chat transcripts for quality and training purposes. We) Tj
T*
(will never ask for your full credit card number, social security number, or account) Tj
T*
(password. If you are ever asked for this information by someone claiming to represent) Tj
T*
(us, do not provide it and report it immediately.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(=============================================================) Tj
T*
(9. FEEDBACK AND QUALITY) Tj
T*
